Psalm 51-5 <t>Behold, <f>ⓚ</f>I was brought forth in iniquity, </t><t>and in sin did my mother conceive me.</t>
Psalm 51-6 <t>Behold, you delight in truth in <f>ⓛ</f>the inward being, </t><t>and you teach me wisdom in the secret heart. </t>
