Psalm 51-15 <t>O Lord, open my lips, </t><t>and my mouth will declare your praise.</t>
Psalm 51-16 <t><f>ⓓ</f> For you will not delight in sacrifice, or I would give it; </t><t>you will not be pleased with a burnt offering.</t>
Psalm 51-17 <t>The sacrifices of God are <f>ⓔ</f>a broken spirit; </t><t>a broken and contrite heart, O God, you will not despise. </t>
